Over time, we intend to expand our development pipeline to include potential treatments for women's health.

FDA Approved Drugs: ORGOVYX (relugolix 120 mg), MYFEMBREE (relugolix 40 mg, estradiol 1.0 mg, and norethindrone acetate 0.5 mg)
